item.title: Kerala HC stays cheating case against Sunny Leone
item.description: Kerala HC stays cheating case against Sunny Leone Kochi: The Kerala High Court Wednesday stayed a cheating case registered against actor Sunny Leone (Karanjit Kaur Vohra) and her husband Daniel Weber.
